    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >这是一个关于人类与机器人走向“终结”的故事。</h2><br>在人类灭亡后的世界里，孤独的机器人【利贝拉】苏醒了。<br>为什么此刻才醒来？为什么身穿白色外套？它被创造出来的意义是什么？<br><br>在行走于荒废世界的旅途中，<br>利贝拉逐渐找回了失落的记忆。<br>最终，它将得知人类所迎来的<strong>“终结”</strong>。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3314030/extras/ecaaeffe7753e20a2919bd852d84aa13.poster.avif?t=1765032906\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3314030/extras/ecaaeffe7753e20a2919bd852d84aa13.webm?t=1765032906\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3314030/extras/ecaaeffe7753e20a2919bd852d84aa13.mp4?t=1765032906\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>──而那，也同样是机器人们的<strong>“终结”</strong>。<br>机器人，是为人而存在的。<br>既然这个世界已无人类，它们也失去了存在的理由。<br><br>当利贝拉最终找回全部记忆时──<br>它静静地关闭了自己的电源。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >与机器人一同行走的末世像素风剧情冒险。</h2><br>《In a World After People》<br>是一款静谧而美丽的<strong>像素风冒险游戏</strong>。<br>玩家将与机器人【利贝拉】一同探索人类灭亡后的世界。<br><br>在探索中，你将收集昔日的记录与遗失的记忆，<br>逐步揭开人类灭亡的真相，以及利贝拉自身的“使命”。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3314030/extras/bb5c0e3ba137cae9be35b2ee9dba81c2.poster.avif?t=1765032906\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3314030/extras/bb5c0e3ba137cae9be35b2ee9dba81c2.webm?t=1765032906\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3314030/extras/bb5c0e3ba137cae9be35b2ee9dba81c2.mp4?t=1765032906\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>调查周围、使用物品、解开小谜题——<br>一段温柔而沉静的游戏体验在等待着你。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >光与影交织而成的荒废像素世界，充满深邃的层次与氛围。</h2><br>本作的特色在于对光影极致讲究的像素画面。<br>闪烁的日光灯、被照亮的空间、<br>以及利贝拉投下的阴影——<br>每一个细节都描绘出失落世界的静谧。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3314030/extras/3aa52d42a3365014671498c16ed1fefb.poster.avif?t=1765032906\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3314030/extras/3aa52d42a3365014671498c16ed1fefb.webm?t=1765032906\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3314030/extras/3aa52d42a3365014671498c16ed1fefb.mp4?t=1765032906\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>一个看似平面，却蕴含深度的世界。<br>在这里，怀旧与新生、孤独与温暖交织共存。<br><br>请在这个世界里，感受<strong>“无人”</strong>所带来的寂寞与美丽。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >关于视频与直播</h2>欢迎录制与直播。<br>请通过右侧“访问网站”查看官方网站的相关指引。<br>同页面亦提供可用于缩略图等的素材下载。",
